      "NodeType": "CodeBlockNode",
      "Code": "inputs;\nwasRun;\nwasCancelled;\n\nisEmpty = List.IsEmpty(inputs);\n\nallowInput = [Imperative]{\nif (isEmpty ==  false)\n\treturn [inputs, true];\nelse\n\treturn [List.Empty, false];\n};\n\n//output\nparamName = allowInput[0][0];\ntoggle = allowInput[1];",
